title: The Engineer
subtitle: I exist and I write code.
about: I am a Full-Stack JavaScript Engineer who loves to build end-to-end products including product concept, planning, design, development, testing, and deployment.

title: The Team Leader
subtitle: A team is a group of people who trust each other.
about: I have met many amazing individuals in tech and I know that this journey has been supported by a supportive community. I have worked on many teams, and I find myself a natural leader, organizer, and delegator.

title: The Idealist
subtitle: Fostering Diverse Thinking in a Multicultural Workplace
about: I have worked on multiple development teams that all had members with different backgrounds and different experiences. This has made me grow as a person and a developer.

title: The Bibliophile
subtitle: Reading gives us someplace to go when we have to stay where we are.
about: I love to read everything, from nonfiction & fiction to comic books & manga to poetry & short stories. Our dog Mia is named after the main character in the Nevernight Trilogy.

title: The Wanderer
subtitle: I haven't been everywhere but it's on my list.
about: I love to travel. Seeing the world, meeting new people, and eating new food are a source of joy in my life. My favorite place is Iceland and my favorite place there is the ice caves. My favorite food there was the Skyr.
